  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed roof alteration, by reason that it would remove part of the main rear roof slope, introduce a rendered elevation with a window that would not align with the windows in the rear elevation of the property and a terrace with a balustrade at roof level, together with the two existing side dormer windows, would result in an overly complex roof form that would detract from the character and appearance of the property and would be incongruous within the terraced row, contrary to policies DM2.1 of Islington's Development Management Policies (2013), policies CS8 and CS9 of Islington's Core Strategy (2011) and the guidance contained within the Islington's Urban Design Guide (2006)."
